%h1= "Hi #{current_user.try(:name)}, welcome to Ask Away!"

.medium-large-text
  %p Here's a few things to know before you start using the site:

  %ol
    %li <strong>Everything happens on the <a href='/'>home page</a>.</strong> Go there to see the top questions of the last few days. Click on a question to answer it. You can answer any questions that your party hasn't answered yet. Just keep in mind if you're the right person in your party to be answering the question.
    %li <strong>We'll send you email reminders</strong> if there are any really popular questions related to your category that you haven't answered yet. Your categories are:
    %li
      <strong>You can invite more people to answer questions</strong> on behalf of The
      = @party.name
      by visiting
      = link_to 'your party\'s page', party_path(@party)
      and clicking 'Invite spokespeople'. You can always get back to your parties page by clicking the icon on the top of the site: (insert image here)
    %li <strong>Have fun!</strong> This is a great opportunity to really connect with Kiwi youth about the things they care about. Also, if you ever have any questions or concerns, don't hesitate to email us (meg@askaway.org.nz).

  = link_to 'Go to the home page!', root_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-lg'
